Pomodoro, a light and concise focusing software. It can help you focus on learning, make learning plans, set meeting reminders, arrange travel plans, and can also be used to record notes and organize shopping lists.

Pomodoro integrates practical functions such as focus, clock-in, reminders, memos, lists, notes, notes, alarms, time management, etc., an application that meets all your needs.

"Efficient Pomodoro"
-Focus: focus on matters, learn efficiently, and develop habits;
-Data analysis: data analysis, tracking problems, and getting rid of bad habits;
-Reminders: remind on time at the set time and place;
-Continuous reminder: stubborn continuous reminder, no longer miss important things;
-Voice input: voice to text, bid farewell to manual input;
-Classification list: simple and clear list, work and life are in order;
-Intelligent time semantic analysis: intelligently analyze the text in text and voice, and intelligently create reminder time;
-Today widget: No need to open the App, quickly view, complete, and create your items in the notification center;
-iCloud synchronization: automatic backup, multi-terminal synchronization, data will no longer be lost;
-Password protection: support digital password, Touch ID, Face ID, protect privacy most professionally;
-Personal settings: you can choose themes, ringtones, button sounds, and vibration feedback according to your preferences;


-------
Obtained high-quality recommended applications by well-known media "Aicheng Technology" and "Neosoft".
